text.tspan: Generic chart title to silence errors
Estimates of the true number of infections. The "upper" and "lower" lines show the bounds of a 95% uncertainty
interval. For comparison, confirmed cases are infections that have been confirmed with a test.
Note: This chart shows the model estimates dated 25 August 2020.
